{"arkId":"cl010116501","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010116501","modified ":"2026-01-14","title":"Montre sph\u00e9rique","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Montre sph\u00e9rique"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Henri II (1547-1559) (Occident-\u003ERenaissance-\u003Edynastie des Valois-Angoul\u00eame)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1551","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 531 - Paul Garnier, Vitrine 2","room":"Salle 531, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1551,"endYear":"","imprecision":"","text":"Milieu du XVIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"De La Garde, Jacques","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"avant 1583","place":"","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"Horloger","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q57727147"}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 7019","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"horlogerie ; montre","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Montre sph\u00e9rique ; bo\u00eetier compos\u00e9 de deux h\u00e9misph\u00e8res s\u0027ouvrant par une charni\u00e8re. Moiti\u00e9 sup\u00e9rieure portant au centre d\u0027une rosace en relief l\u0027anneau de suspension ; en partie ajour\u00e9e, grav\u00e9e de croissants et de volutes parmi lesquels apparaissent des mascarons. Partie inf\u00e9rieure pleine, grav\u00e9e d\u0027entrelacs, d\u0027arabesques, de feuillages sur un fond stri\u00e9. Cadran \u00e0 chiffres romains situ\u00e9 en retrait \u00e0 l\u0027int\u00e9rieur d\u0027un cercle servant de socle. Muni d\u0027une aiguille en acier dont la marche est ponctu\u00e9e par douze rayons grav\u00e9s. Mouvement dot\u00e9 d\u0027une sonnerie au passage des heures retentissant sur un timbre log\u00e9 dans l\u0027h\u00e9misph\u00e8re sup\u00e9rieur. Poss\u00e9dant deux barillets, un \u00e9chappement \u00e0 roue de rencontre, un foliot annulaire, une fus\u00e9e \u00e0 corde \u00e0 boyau. Cl\u00e9 de remontage dite \u00e0 manivelle conserv\u00e9e.","inscriptions":"Inscription : \r ; lettre S d\u00e9sginant le trou de remontage de la sonnerie \r ; Signature : \r ; mouvement sign\u00e9 et dat\u00e9 : JACQUES\/DELAGARDE\/BLOYS 1551","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"5,5","displayDimension":"5,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"6,4","displayDimension":"6,4 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : fer\r\nMat\u00e9riau : laiton","placeOfCreation":"Blois (Centre-\u003ELoir-et-Cher = Loir et Cher)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"collection Paul Garnier (1834-1916), \u00e0 Paris. Don Paul Garnier, en 1916.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"M. Garnier, Paul ","note":"","role":", Donateur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"don","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date du d\u00e9cret","value":"19\/06\/1916","startYear":1916,"endYear":1916}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"don"}],"period":[{"value":"Henri II (1547-1559)"}],"place":[{"value":"Blois"}],"objectType":[{"value":"horlogerie"},{"value":"montre"}]},"bibliography":[{"bibliographyRef":"Cardinal, Catherine, Les montres et horloges de table du mus\u00e9e du Louvre, Tome 2, Paris, RMN, 2000","bibliographyDate":"2000","bibliograph